post_text: Box Tops for Education is transitioning to clip-less. For the next year, you can still send in the Box Tops we are all used to. However, please also download the Box Tops App. All you need to do is create an account, choose Island Elementary School, and scan your receipts. If you have purchased a Box Tops item, our school will get credit. No more poring over and cutting out all the little Box Tops! Just scan your receipt! (And while you are scanning- also scan the same receipt for Shoparoo...we get money for any and all scans of receipts). Win-Win! (Also, until the transition is done in the next year- we can double dip with those items that have a hard Box Top by cutting it out AND scanning the receipt! Woohoo!

post_text:
We were able to celebrate our awesome staff last week for Teacher Appreciation Week! Our Sunshine committee came up with an amazing lineup for the week:
Monday- "Donut" what we'd do without you!!
Tuesday- Thank you card stations were set up for students to write cards to all of Island staff for all they do.
Wednesday- Hungry Bear cookies were delivered for a sweet treat.
Thursday- Bath Bombs were left out for all of island staff since they are "the bomb."
Friday- Was a rolling celebration of Thanks for the whole staff to celebrate a year of hard work!!

Thanks Island Staff for being amazing! Thanks Audra Coelho for chairing Sunshine and your amazing ideas.
